{"tid":1675430,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"尿道炎有冇得斷尾","createTime":"2019-10-26T01:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T16:35:52.000Z","uid":266668,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"423c4efe0fb3b1669cfa097eb11c49a83d6c69ae","tid":1675430,"uid":266668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:13:38.000Z","msg":"一年都翻發過好多次，次次都係食藥等佢好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩嘅就兩日，呢次就快一星期都未好<br />\n食抗生素同小便會變深色嗰隻尿道炎藥(試過兩種)都覺得冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係得個等字 等佢好翻，隔一排又黎過<br />\n<br />\n同埋女仔嘅話 啲醫生會同你講做完之後要去小便，沖身反而會沖左啲菌入尿道 膀胱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我雖然冇去小便，但過幾日先會 甚至冇做都會翻發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以都唔知邊到出問題<br />\n<br />\n第一次有事係得尿急感 但小便唔痛，所以醫生話唔係尿道炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />照左超聲波驗過幾次小便都check 唔到究竟邊到出問題，淨係講唔關我身體結構事"},{"pid":"409292d572b6479e572c561a0704a813374b5114","tid":1675430,"uid":8726,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"比我插下就會好番"},{"pid":"ff93e0a775cd734ed445337957689785f5a38bec","tid":1675430,"uid":266668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"409292d572b6479e572c561a0704a813374b5114","tid":1675430,"uid":8726,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"比我插下就會好番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:29:58.000Z","msg":"成日都見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真問架"},{"pid":"3171ccbfd6b818c582d3166a42a0e6017651048d","tid":1675430,"uid":8726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ff93e0a775cd734ed445337957689785f5a38bec","tid":1675430,"uid":266668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"409292d572b6479e572c561a0704a813374b5114","tid":1675430,"uid":8726,"like":6,"dislike":20,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"比我插下就會好番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26